    "You have not created any upload links yet. An upload link allows anyone to upload files to a folder or library. You can create an upload link for a folder or library by clicking the share icon to the right of its name.": "Du har inte skapat en uppladdningsl\u00e4nk \u00e4nnu. En uppladdningsl\u00e4nk till\u00e5ter vem som helst att ladda upp filer till en mapp eller katalog. Du kan skapa en uppladdningsl\u00e4nk f\u00f6r en mapp eller katalog genom att klicka p\u00e5 delningsikonen till h\u00f6ger om dess namn.",
    "You have not deleted any libraries in the last {placeholder} days. A deleted library will be cleaned automatically after this period.": "Du har inte tagit bort n\u00e5gra kataloger de senaste {placeholder} dagar. En borttagen katalog kommer att rensas automatiskt efter denna period.",
    "You have not invited any guests yet. A guest can access shared libraries through the web interface allowing more efficient ways to collaborate than through links. You can invite a guest by clicking the \"Invite Guest\" item in the dropdown menu.": "You have not invited any guests yet. A guest can access shared libraries through the web interface allowing more efficient ways to collaborate than through links. You can invite a guest by clicking the \"Invite Guest\" item in the dropdown menu.",
